snippet: In 2010, Tyrone S. Woods began working with security details protecting diplomatic personnel, from Central America to the Middle East.
abstract: Dr Timothy Rasmusson, former brother-in-law of Tyrone S Woods, one of four Americans killed in attack on diplomatic compound in Benghazi, Libya, describes Woods as a Navy SEALs veteran with a compulsive need for adrenaline.
